`` Everybody Needs a Best Friend '' is a song from the 2012 feature film Ted , with music composed by Walter Murphy and lyrics by Seth MacFarlane .
Performed by Norah Jones during the film 's opening credits , the song was used as the film 's main theme song .
It was released by Universal Republic Records on June 26 , 2012 .
In January 2013 , the song was nominated for the Academy Award for Best Original Song at the 85th Academy Awards , but lost to `` Skyfall '' from the film of the same name .
MacFarlane was also the host of the Oscars while also being nominated .